    • Method Detail

      • build

        public com.google.api.ads.adwords.jaxws.v201309.cm.Selector build()
        Builds a new Selector. When a Selector is built by this method, the state of the builder doesn't change. If you need to clean the builder, the best way to do it, is by creating a new instance.
        Returns:
        the new Selector containing all the configuration that was set previously.

      • fields

        public SelectorBuilder fields(String... fields)
        Chooses the set of fields that will be selected via the API. Calling this method multiple times will overwrite the previous fields that were set.
        Parameters:
        fields - the set of fields of the given entity.
        Returns:
        the builder itself to proceed the chain.
